casebody.data:
MOTION DOCKET

91-1355. In re Application of Lammers.

Sua sponte, Maximillian P. Lammers, Jr. is granted leave to file objections instanter; this cause is set for hearing.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes and Douglas, JJ., concur. Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., would immediately suspend his license pending his receipt of a law degree.
